{"TopicId":216069,"ForumId":119,"TopicTitle":"Vote for how you feel about KSP 2","CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-30T11:59:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-30T11:59:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLets see what the community has to say, with these three questions:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAre you happy with KSP 2 so far? \u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E(from release to current version)\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAre you excited and hopeful for the future of KSP 2 and its upcoming planned updates?\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EWhen the game was first released, what was your opinion of the game? \u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E(multiple choice)\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a debate and there is no right or wrong answer(s)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like polls\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-30T12:44:02Z\u0022 title=\u002203/30/2023 12:44  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 30, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Tazooka\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003ETypo\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HenryBlatbugIII","CreatedById":159624,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-30T12:25:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t bought it yet, and I don\u0027t plan to until it looks like a game I\u0027d want to play.\u00A0 I\u0027m keeping up with the news to see when the game reaches that point, and I\u0027m hopeful that it will happen after the Science, Colonies, or Resources updates.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-30T12:46:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224267319\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216069\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680179129\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HenryBlatbugIII\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, HenryBlatbugIII said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI haven\u0027t bought it yet, and I don\u0027t plan to until it looks like a game I\u0027d want to play.\u00A0 I\u0027m keeping up with the news to see when the game reaches that point, and I\u0027m hopeful that it will happen after the Science, Colonies, or Resources updates.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for your thoughts \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EYou should be able to vote if you haven\u0027t already as I made sure to have a\u00A0 \u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:14px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EI didn\u0027t get the game\u0022 option\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lyneira","CreatedById":149515,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-01T07:17:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI voted \u0022Neutral\u0022 for my happiness with KSP2, but that\u0027s really just a stand-in for a mixed bag of feelings on different parts of the game. I\u0027m happy with the graphical foundation and the soundtrack, but not (yet) with the play experience with many missing features and parts from KSP1 and the bugs we\u0027ve had to deal with and are still dealing with.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt should come as no surprise then that I ticked several checkboxes that might seem a bit contradictory like \u0022Better than KSP1\u0022 as well as \u0022Disappointed\u0022, \u0022Excited to be part of early access\u0022 and \u0022It looks amazing.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDespite the parts I\u0027m not happy with, I have been able to enjoy the game while setting some non-ambitious goals that avoid interactions the game isn\u0027t quite ready for yet, like vessel switching and docking and undocking. Part of what holds me back from going interplanetary to explore the other planets is my own mindset of optimizing for low cost in KSP1 career mode, which has led to optimizing for low mass and sticking with low tech options for space missions rather than just using the nuclear parts for what they\u0027re meant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-04-01T07:32:58Z\u0022 title=\u002204/01/2023 07:32  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EApril 1, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by Lyneira\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-01T19:27:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRr3TaALZfoK0QqfRxxslZ\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.00\u0022 height=\u0022168\u0022 width=\u0022300\u0022 src=\u0022https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRr3TaALZfoK0QqfRxxslZ8quyBzMy33c2Shw\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not voting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-03T13:08:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224268092\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216069\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680377245\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/1/2023 at 8:27 PM, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRr3TaALZfoK0QqfRxxslZ8quyBzMy33c2Shw\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRr3TaALZfoK0QqfRxxslZ\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002256.00\u0022 height=\u0022168\u0022 width=\u0022300\u0022 src=\u0022https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRr3TaALZfoK0QqfRxxslZ8quyBzMy33c2Shw\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not voting.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022Neutral Neutral Neutral\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsAttachLink_image\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022100.00\u0022 height=\u0022800\u0022 style=\u0022width:100px;height:auto;\u0022 width=\u0022800\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/Flag_of_Switzerland_(Pantone).svg/800px-Flag_of_Switzerland_(Pantone).svg.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-03T13:16:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to visit Switzerland, yes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Fluke","CreatedById":205590,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-03T18:19:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHighly recommend Grindelwald!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224268590\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022216069\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680527809\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to visit Switzerland, yes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHighly recommend Grindelwald!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}